title: S.O.S 'n' Trolling For Cadavers Split e.p. Album
description:
We've waited almost two years for the collaboration of these stellar titans...and the wait is over! Here, now, is presented...the split e.p./album by none other than S.O.S (Scumbags of Society) and Trolling For Cadavers! This monumental piece of sheer brilliance features the S.O.S e.p. entitled "Diggin' Ditches For Bitches" and the e.p. contribution of Trolling For Cadavers called "Dead Sexxy"!

MP3 (320 kbps)

Songs included are:

"Rape 'Em All!" (S.O.S)
"Diggin' Ditches For Bitches" (S.O.S)
"Workin' Overtime/Here Cums the Digger" (S.O.S)
"Hurtin' For a Squirtin'" (S.O.S)

"The Bone Orchard" (Trolling For Cadavers)
"Praise the Blaze" (Trolling For Cadavers)
"Severed Heads and Savage Grins" (Trolling For Cadavers)
"Dandelions in December" (Trolling For Cadavers)
"Dead Sexxy" (Trolling For Cadavers)

Enjoy and Destroy!
